---
title: Double Seared Beef Rump & Dijon Onion Gravy with Mash & Roasted Root Veggies
description: Long after you finish this dinner of steak and three veg, you're going to remember the way it was transformed by the simple
addition of a luscious mustard sauce. It's an easy trick that gives this classic dish a new lease on life.
